The planet [[Olanet]] was the site of a massive [[Confederacy of Independent Systems/Legends|Separatist]] '''droid factory'''. It was said to be one of the largest producer of [[Battle droid/Legends|battle droids]] besides [[Geonosis/Legends|Geonosis]]. In [[21 BBY/Legends|21 BBY]], the factory was [[Sabotage of Olanet Droid Factory|sabotaged]] by [[Clone trooper/Legends|clone troopers]] [[Prudii Skirata|N-5]] and [[Atin Skirata|RC-3222]].

